Mails, letters, msgs , tags pyarrrr tm logo ne garima ko dia!! PATA nai tha  ke mere chracter ko itna pyar doge tm log! I remember being nervous and under confident before facing a film camera for the first time in my life. But the moment, camera rolled, I felt like there was no camera in the room! Like its my space!  Warmth , comfort and so much more to learn everyday under the best director @instaprashant , producers who put their blind faith on a completely new talent @mamtayashpatnaik @yashpatnaikofficial and my co-actors who became friendsss in no good days! @ashishraghava @khedkarshivangi @mihirahuja_ And ofc our talented editor @reelcutwaala who made me look amazing! @amazonmxplayer @mxplayer for being the most entertaining OTT ♥️ And the entire team for making Garima act, look, behave and be a fit! I love you all.
